 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601861f32c5936c7348e08328228a87f4b70ad9d","tid":981146,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:23:06.000Z","msg":"點止，根本直頭要唔俾退休後做受薪工作添啦<br />\n你睇幾多高官退休但轉頭又出去俾大集團安個乜乜顧問非執董，擺明延後利益<br />\n又唔見做私人工嘅退休後啲公司仲會咁樣請返？（除咗老闆啲皇親國戚）<br />\n退得休如果出去受薪根本應該要cut長俸"},{"pid":"fea1106b29620750b2eb5e1f8db3c0020bc3eb8a","tid":981146,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"退休都有人工收真係戇鳩又無貢獻  私人企業都算<br />\n<br />\n公務員長糧咪即係要我地市民既血汗錢"},{"pid":"23470111412b9c3dcb1d46d1e38ba7d633317053","tid":981146,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:25:32.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"01c91054457fcfdbb421d79c885b3ba480bf5165","tid":981146,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:26:57.000Z","msg":"販民提私人草案啦"},{"pid":"c6504dc3dd24f0f4962e3a0d906e2317102b077b","tid":981146,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:28:22.000Z","msg":"舊制果班大部份都係垃圾<br />\n唔升得響度都袋幾舊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36338c5f9421b537bbdaf892d95cac33ca911668","tid":981146,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"局長級係撚公務員咩，問責官員呀<br />\n公務員最高級都係常任秘書長咋"},{"pid":"f4802442e202b94ccba2d3d0abbc242abf883017","tid":981146,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"36338c5f9421b537bbdaf892d95cac33ca911668","tid":981146,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"局長級係撚公務員咩，問責官員呀<br />\n公務員最高級都係常任秘書長咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"sorry講得唔清楚<br />\n指有長俸個d翻閹問責司局長特首<br />\n又食又拎,自己so左仲要搞窮人講風良話"},{"pid":"82909a489acecac152dab1541410302725c51485","tid":981146,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4802442e202b94ccba2d3d0abbc242abf883017","tid":981146,